<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#fromPort> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#fromPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#Navigability> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#fromPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#Port> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#fromPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Port from which the navigability relation starts: conventionally, the \"exit port\" from which a running train leaves a net element."@en .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#fromPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "from port"@en .
# 
