<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#leadsTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#leadsToTransitive> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#leadsTo> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyChainAxiom> _:genid4 .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid3 .
