<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/topology/topo#navigableTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Expresses the possibility, for a train movement, to leave a net element via an exit port and to navigate to another net element until another exit port. Navigation excludes reversal of travel direction, even if the reversal is allowed by operational rules (e.g. shunting mode, ...)."@en .
