<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasMetricLength> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#hasMetricLength> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasMetricLength> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#LinearThings> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasMetricLength> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> .
