# 
# https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasNominalMetricLength
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasNominalMetricLength> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasNominalMetricLength> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/adapters/geosparql_adapter/geo_ad#hasMetricLength> .
